room_title: Escape room "Classroom" by Escape Muncie in Muncie
review: Loved it! Very creative and strategic puzzles. It was so fun to do the puzzles and clues. Our group of 3 did the classroom and almost solved it. Can't wait to go back again for the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Classroom" by Escape Muncie in Muncie
review: The Classroom game is well-organized, challenging, and fun! We had a group of seven, and the room kept all of us engaged and working together on our escape! Bonus: the owners are incredibly nice and proceeds support their favorite charity.

room_title: Escape room "Classroom" by Escape Muncie in Muncie
review: We had a great time working The Classroom. Very fun time with the family.
